@host = https://localhost:7201

### ===================================
### Demo 1: Calm Seas — Resilience Fundamentals
### ===================================

### Get sea conditions via resilient client
### (Downstream fails ~40% — retries and circuit breaker kick in)
GET {{host}}/voyage/calm-seas
Accept: application/json

### ===================================
### Demo 2: Rough Seas — Chaos Injection
### ===================================

### Fault Injection — 50% chance of HttpRequestException
GET {{host}}/voyage/rough-seas/faults
Accept: application/json

### Latency Injection — 50% chance of 3-second delay
GET {{host}}/voyage/rough-seas/latency
Accept: application/json

### Outcome Injection — 50% chance of HTTP 500
GET {{host}}/voyage/rough-seas/outcomes
Accept: application/json

### ===================================
### Demo 3: Game Day — Feature Flag Chaos
### ===================================

### Check current feature flag status
GET {{host}}/voyage/game-day/status
Accept: application/json

### Trigger game day voyage (chaos gated by feature flags)
GET {{host}}/voyage/game-day
Accept: application/json

### ===================================
### OpenAPI
### ===================================

### Get OpenAPI document
GET {{host}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json
